snippet: Lucie Safarova grabbed the last spot at the WTA Finals in Singapore after Carla Suárez Navarro lost, 6-1, 6-2, to the qualifier Daria Kasatkina at the Kremlin Cup.
abstract: Lucie Safarova secures spot in WTA Finals when Carla Suarez Navarro loses at Kremlin Cup to Daria Kasatkina; other tennis results noted.
